29 Alabama.
30 Section 2. In accordance with Section 11-42-6 of the
31 Code of Alabama 1975, a map showing the proposed territory to
32 be altered, rearranged, and extended from the City of
33 Demopolis is on file and open to public inspection in the
34 office of the Judge of Probate in Marengo County, Alabama.
35 Section 3. This act shall become effective on October
36 1, 2026.
